column3: str

Stigma-4 has received a new directive to spice things up at the café.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
Speak with the alimentary survey unit.
Deliver the requested ingredients to the alimentary survey unit.
Report to Stigma-4.
Speak with the alimentary survey unit.

<If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),16))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Mine <SheetEn(Item,3,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> to the alimentary survey unit.</If><Else/><If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),17))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Gather <SheetEn(Item,3,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> to the alimentary survey unit.</If><Else/><If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),18))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Catch <SheetEn(Item,1,IntegerParameter(5),1,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),1,1)/> to the alimentary survey unit.</If><Else/></If></If></If>
Report to Stigma-4.
The furry café owner has proposed a plan to secure more customers─a reconfiguration of the food directory.
Specifically, the creation of a food item comprised of materials from the Elysian seas and suited to Karellian proclivities has been requested.
Your assistance is required. Please report to the alimentary survey unit for further instruction.
Provision supplier identified: <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>. Loading entry for Karellian cuisine production...
Based on data from Karellian survey, certain diatom clusters have been determined to optimize “delectable” quotient while also promoting healthy digestion.
Based on data from Karellian survey, certain rock moss has been determined to optimize “delectable” quotient while also promoting healthy digestion.
Based on data from Karellian survey, the aquatic organism colloquially referred to as “seaweed snapper” has been determined to optimize “delectable” quotient while also promoting healthy digestion.
Use of gold salmon roe is strongly recommended for procurement. All proceeds go to Omicron enhancement initiatives.
Please proceed to the marked area for acquisition. Prompt delivery is advised to ensure preservation of nutritional value.

Loading directive... <whirr>
Please procure diatom clusters to optimize “delectable” quotient and promote healthy digestion.

Loading directive... <whirr>
Please procure rock moss to optimize “delectable” quotient and promote healthy digestion.

Loading directive... <whirr>
Please procure seaweed snapper to optimize “delectable” quotient and promote healthy digestion.
Prompt delivery is advised to ensure preservation of nutritional value. Please note that further delays may result in severe disappointment.
Welcome back, <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>. Please insert delivery to continue.

Scanning... <whirr> Scanning...
Quality of ingredients is acceptable. Delivery complete.
Please return to Stigma-4 to receive compensation.
Return confirmed. Your timely delivery of goods has been noted and is greatly appreciated.
This successful addition to the café's food directory should appease the fuzzy one for the time being.
<beep> Warning: extensive diversification of food directory likely to result in logistical errors. Standardization of customer digestive organs advised as the most efficient solution.
